{
  "stem": "20021.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you had to be good at it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as time went on, I apparently became good at it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Tell me about your father and your brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, my father was hiding out in a place, for which he was paying big money, just so that this-- this woman was hiding him out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But one day, she had to move from that place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Germans-- they were enlarging the base.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a military base, an airplane base, and so whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they issued an edict, everybody from this area has to move.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father had nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He couldn't find another place to hide out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew at that point about that-- about the possibility of going to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because a friend of mine-- who by the way also underwent the same operation from the same surgeon-- went to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He went in May, and wrote me a card.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We agreed on a certain code, which would indicate that it's safe to do this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he wrote me back a card from Budapest that he arrived to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I knew about this possibility.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And here my father, being totally exposed-- in other words, he would have perished right there and then.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because he could not do what I did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A, he didn't have yet the papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to arrange for forged papers at that point became more and more difficult, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Plus, he just didn't have the looks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Plus, he didn't have the-- the-- the-- the means to play that game.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, he was maybe too old, and it just wouldn't have worked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, he was the reason that I went to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
